Jack Conway (filmmaker) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_Conway_(filmmaker) 0 Jack Ryan Conway (July 17, 1887 – October 11, 1952) was an American film director and film producer, as well as an actor of many films in the first half of the 20th century.
